    "markdown": "---\ntitle: \"\"\nruntime: shiny\ntoc: false\n---\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n::: country-hero-text\n<h1 class=\"country-title\">\n\n\n\n</h1>\n\n<h2>Geocoded Health Facilities for Malaria Modelling</h2>\n\n<p>Standardized, geolocated facility information to strengthen modelling, planning, and decision-making</p>\n\n:::::\n\n<!-- ===================== -->\n\n<!-- Map + Section Navigation -->\n\n<!-- ===================== -->\n\n:::: {.columns .country-main}\n::: {.column width=\"70%\"}\n## Health Facilities Map\n\n\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"leaflet html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-cf57dac70ab49e4e4ab7\" style=\"width:100%;height:464px;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-cf57dac70ab49e4e4ab7\">{\"x\":{\"options\":{\"crs\":{\"crsClass\":\"L.CRS.EPSG3857\",\"code\":null,\"proj4def\":null,\"projectedBounds\":null,\"options\":{}}},\"calls\":[{\"method\":\"addTiles\",\"args\":[\"https://{s}.tile.openstreetmap.org/{z}/{x}/{y}.png\",null,null,{\"minZoom\":0,\"maxZoom\":18,\"tileSize\":256,\"subdomains\":\"abc\",\"errorTileUrl\":\"\",\"tms\":false,\"noWrap\":false,\"zoomOffset\":0,\"zoomReverse\":false,\"opacity\":1,\"zIndex\":1,\"detectRetina\":false,\"attribution\":\"&copy; <a href=\\\"https://openstreetmap.org/copyright/\\\">OpenStreetMap<\\/a>,  <a href=\\\"https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/\\\">ODbL<\\/a>\"}]},{\"method\":\"addCircleMarkers\",\"args\":[[-2.64496,-2.44682,-3.55117,-9.501390000000001,-7.19919,-1.30831,-5.07611],[34.01009,32.1526,33.69935,33.3476,39.0225,33.964,39.10071],3,null,null,{\"interactive\":true,\"className\":\"\",\"stroke\":false,\"color\":\"#03F\",\"weight\":5,\"opacity\":0.5,\"fill\":true,\"fillColor\":\"#03F\",\"fillOpacity\":0.7},null,null,null,null,null,{\"interactive\":false,\"permanent\":false,\"direction\":\"auto\",\"opacity\":1,\"offset\":[0,0],\"textsize\":\"10px\",\"textOnly\":false,\"className\":\"\",\"sticky\":true},null]}],\"limits\":{\"lat\":[-9.501390000000001,-1.30831],\"lng\":[32.1526,39.10071]}},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n\n:::\n:::\n\n\n\n:::\n\n:::{.column width=\"30%\" .toc-panel}\n\n### On this page\n\n- [Overview](#overview)\n- [Demographics](#demographics)\n- [Services](#services)\n- [Data Download](#data-download)\n\n\n:::\n\n::::\n\n\n## Overview {#overview}\n\nThis section gives a general summary of health facilities in Tanzania.  \nYou can include charts, stats, or key messages here.\n\n## Demographics {#demographics}\n\nHere you display facility-level demographic info, e.g., number of beds, staff, population served, etc.\n\n## Services {#services}\n\nDetails of available services per facility, e.g., outpatient, malaria, maternal health, HIV services.\n\n## Data Download {#data-download}\n\nProvide links for users to download:\n\n- [CSV](../data/tanzania/hf_demographics.csv)  \n- [JSON](../data/tanzania/hf_demographics.json)  \n- [RDS](../data/tanzania/hf_demographic_sf.rds)\n",
